Package: agronomymap
Title: Spatial Heatmap Visualization for Agronomic Field Trials
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("JK", "Kim", , "kimjk@agronomy4future.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for generating heatmaps and spatial field visualizations
    from agronomic trial data, including raster interpolation, point overlays,
    and customizable axis labeling. Designed for agricultural researchers
    working with grid-based field layouts (row/column).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
